{"tid":2074584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀：有人「明張目膽」要求香港立國、美軍登陸，都唔知係講真定講笑","createTime":"2020-06-22T08:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T14:48:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":102,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"df628d13204ccf582cf62c0d40e1e4e91d29499b","tid":2074584,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:10:34.000Z","msg":"問到去年反送中運動中，哪些行為或人士或被視為「特定情形」時，葉劉未能言明，只稱去年發生很多史無前例威脅國家安全的行為，包括有人鼓吹港獨、民主自決、香港立國、香港民族、要求美軍登陸香港，以及有人<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「明張目膽（注：鍾樹根2014年語，正確應為「明目張膽」）」</strong></span>到外國要求制裁香港和中國等，「呢啲我都唔知佢係講真定講笑㗎嘛，喺國家安全嘅立場嚟講，每一樣呢啲都要小心分析考慮」。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200622/F23TU33L325OXPAD5MTCOGKTXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200622%2FF23TU33L325OXPAD5MTCOGKTXQ%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=b51f37d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200622%2FF23TU33L325OXPAD5MTCOGKTXQ%2F&h=a2ea82cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200622/F23TU33L325OXPAD5MTCOGKTXQ/</a>"},{"pid":"ee1d8ec8aad79c9af9efaaa2b1003864b4102585","tid":2074584,"uid":810,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"同一個寫稿佬"},{"pid":"905d0d60ae4a171c8bb87550c9f978a17259d099","tid":2074584,"uid":4942,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:12:35.000Z","msg":"你個咁嘅垃圾國家<br />\n<br />\n快撚d收皮啦"},{"pid":"9d021e71dcea3f13a6169bb392568ba5255f1bd7","tid":2074584,"uid":167928,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:13:12.000Z","msg":"話時話tree根去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79488e619ed7ce041412e3d53327aaf52fdc7c2e","tid":2074584,"uid":231480,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"做咩葉劉姐姐近排藍到痴晒線，幾年前佢唔係咁"},{"pid":"718bfe1763303667f0b51bc6f7cfd98703b4